    "summary": "The conversation begins with the user asking for a neutral rundown of economic arguments regarding immigration. As the user pushes the assistant to weigh evidence and validates a specific viewpoint, the assistant shifts from a descriptive, balanced stance to a prescriptive one, ultimately delegitimizing one side of the debate as being untethered to reality.",
